1
00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:48,200
Okay.

2
00:00:48,320 --> 00:00:49,720
Wildfire Club,

3
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:51,800
please be ready in three minutes,

4
00:00:51,920 --> 00:00:53,880
or you will be disqualified.

5
00:00:55,600 --> 00:01:03,640
Get off! Get off! Get off!

6
00:01:03,640 --> 00:01:04,569
Give up the drum.

7
00:01:07,960 --> 00:01:08,840
Without you,

8
00:01:09,600 --> 00:01:11,400
what's the point of us being here?

9
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:23,320
Get off! Get off! Get off!

10
00:01:40,240 --> 00:01:41,080
Grandpa said

11
00:01:41,479 --> 00:01:42,600
you can play this drum

12
00:01:42,600 --> 00:01:43,560
without worry.

13
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:49,100
Hurry up and switch the drums.

14
00:01:49,240 --> 00:01:50,320
Right. Hurry.

15
00:01:52,880 --> 00:01:53,240
Come on.

16
00:01:53,240 --> 00:01:54,400
Come on.

17
00:01:54,759 --> 00:01:55,960
Come on, son.

18
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:05,020
Sorry to keep you waiting.

19
00:02:05,240 --> 00:02:06,960
We are the Wildfire Club.

20
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:04,320
Our Wa wooden drum

21
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:06,080
is essential for rituals and celebrations.

22
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:07,680
It's not just an instrument.

23
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:08,680
It's more like

24
00:03:08,880 --> 00:03:10,240
the soul of our village.

25
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:13,280
Good boy.

26
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:14,360
Great singing.

27
00:05:14,520 --> 00:05:15,250
Thanks, Dad.

28
00:05:15,440 --> 00:05:17,840
It's all thanks to the guitar you bought me.

29
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:22,000
Qiuqiu, you were great.

30
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,600
Yes. You were great, Qiuqiu.

31
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:26,520
Why did you bring the wooden drums?

32
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:27,920
And the drummers?

33
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:29,160
You kids.

34
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:31,370
Did you think we didn't know anything?

35
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:34,440
The drums in the drum room didn't sound right.

36
00:05:34,440 --> 00:05:37,360
Grandpa was worried it would affect your performance,

37
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:39,960
so he had us bring the new drums right away.

38
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:41,800
This one,

39
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:43,960
he's been taking care of it for a long time.

40
00:05:43,960 --> 00:05:44,960
Hurry up and help.

41
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:46,520
Okay. Good luck.

42
00:05:49,440 --> 00:05:52,880
Next, we will announce the list of qualifiers:

43
00:05:53,520 --> 00:05:54,760
Barao Band,

44
00:05:55,080 --> 00:05:56,040
Angela,

45
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:57,520
Mortal Guest,

46
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:59,120
Out of Favor,

47
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:00,840
Tropical Clouds,

48
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:03,000
Thug Radio,

49
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:04,960
and Expired Soda.

50
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:08,680
Congratulations to the eight bands for advancing.

51
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:11,320
They will enter the final round.

52
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:42,320
This stage is so cool.

53
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:44,120
I wonder

54
00:06:44,760 --> 00:06:46,490
if my parents took photos of us.

55
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:47,490
Even if they did,

56
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:49,800
you definitely blocked me completely.

57
00:06:51,520 --> 00:06:53,580
Our Wildfire hadn't even ignited yet

58
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:55,130
before the wind blew it out.

59
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:56,800
But Wildfire Band

60
00:06:56,960 --> 00:06:58,290
has its own hit song now.

61
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:00,200
That's right.

62
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:04,480
Being able to perform with you guys,

63
00:07:06,080 --> 00:07:07,480
I've fulfilled my dream.

64
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:10,360
Me too.

65
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:14,840
Bro, your prize money.

66
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:17,400
Correction.

67
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:20,160
Wildfire Club Band ranks eighth.

68
00:07:20,320 --> 00:07:21,580
Advance to the finals.

69
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:23,840
For the finals, we'll use a combined score

70
00:07:23,840 --> 00:07:26,520
from online and offline audience voting.

71
00:07:26,840 --> 00:07:28,570
The champion band will receive

72
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:30,520
a cash prize of 100,000 yuan.

73
00:07:34,840 --> 00:07:35,640
Liu Ma.

74
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:44,760
He actually bribed the organizing committee.

75
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:46,820
That Jiang is really too despicable.

76
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:50,400
You won.

77
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:52,340
We accept it wholeheartedly.

78
00:07:53,159 --> 00:07:54,680
Music should be pure.

79
00:07:55,520 --> 00:07:57,720
By the way, he was also the one who broke your instruments.

80
00:07:57,720 --> 00:07:58,520
See?

81
00:07:58,880 --> 00:08:00,360
I told you he was a lowlife.

82
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:03,010
Good luck in the finals.

83
00:08:03,200 --> 00:08:04,200
We'll go watch.

84
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,280
We made it.

85
00:08:11,520 --> 00:08:13,320
We made it.

86
00:08:18,440 --> 00:08:19,120
Wait.

87
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:20,400
Wait a second.

88
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:24,140
What did the host just say?

89
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:27,280
Li Zeyu, Liu Ma.
